REM Title: Toggle dark mode
REM Author: Cypher
REM Description: Flips macOS appearance between Light and Dark via osascript.
REM Target: macOS 10.14+
DELAY 500
GUI SPACE
DELAY 500
STRING Terminal
DELAY 1000
ENTER
DELAY 800
STRING osascript -e 'tell app "System Events" to tell appearance preferences to set dark mode to not dark mode'
ENTER
